dct_description_sm: Shows: Moscow city limits (approximately); 2 classes of roads, and railroad in the metropolitan area and inner region. "801483 4-90." Ancillary map: Moscow Oblast. Scale [approximately 1:2,160,000], showing oblast and rayon boundaries. Inset map shows oblast, rayon, and administrative center boundaries.
